{"tid":1962630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2021年起每名前線軍裝黑警都會有隨身cam","createTime":"2020-04-07T14:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T03:05:35.000Z","uid":135274,"like":8,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"47bebefa849553d66c0d8b996bf050ef7d4272fd","tid":1962630,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/警方-反修例運動用逾-1-6-萬枚催淚彈-1400-樽胡椒噴劑-實彈-19-發-用警棍僅-104-次/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A8%E9%80%BE-1-6-%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%9A%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-1400-%E6%A8%BD%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%99%B4%E5%8A%91-%E5%AF%A6%E5%BD%88-19-%E7%99%BC-%E7%94%A8%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E5%83%85-104-%E6%AC%A1%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=29612480\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A8%E9%80%BE-1-6-%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%9A%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-1400-%E6%A8%BD%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%99%B4%E5%8A%91-%E5%AF%A6%E5%BD%88-19-%E7%99%BC-%E7%94%A8%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E5%83%85-104-%E6%AC%A1%2F&h=10e80ef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/警方-反修例運動用逾-1-6-萬枚催淚彈-1400-樽胡椒噴劑-實彈-19-發-用警棍僅-104-次/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，警方指預計於 2021年落實為每位前線軍裝警員配備隨身攝錄機。警方補充，去年警隊曾於超過 300 宗個案中使用隨身攝錄機，共錄得超過 420 段片段中，有 72 段曾被用作調查或舉證用途。警方說，在預計可能會發生對抗場面或破壞社會安寧事件中，警隊使用隨身攝錄機能有效產生降溫和約束作用，以防止違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n警方說現有超過 3300 部隨身攝錄機，並計劃在來年添置 4500 部，以加強警員的搜證能力及提升行動效率。"},{"pid":"3d5ecdd2b5ebfb322e78bcd2cef4879a051cfb21","tid":1962630,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56b352646bf2c7410d13edc0bb14295cab58863","tid":1962630,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re